everybody welcome to church it's good to be with you all of you that have gathered in the room and those of you watching online you could be anywhere and you're here you're joining us and we're so glad that you are here and I'm telling you everybody you picked a good day to be in church this is also the weekend that I say no mascara because it's baptism weekend and our eyes are about to be blessed

