Take a look at this.

14:23.842 --> 14:53.714
Listen, I show that because if that's how you're going to be watching football later, your one job today is to bring that same energy, passion and excitement to this church today because today hundreds of people are stepping into these baptism waters to publicly declare their faith in Jesus Christ and we are here to celebrate.

14:54.338 --> 14:55.460
But yes.

15:01.167 --> 15:07.716
But there is another group here today, a group of people that didn't plan on coming to get baptized.

15:08.537 --> 15:21.074
They don't have a change of clothes, no towel, no expectation, but our prayer has been from the moment that you walked in or joined us online, that God would start whispering, nudging, stirring something in your heart.

15:21.730 --> 15:27.438
And that at some point today, you're going to decide, I'm getting baptized.

15:27.458 --> 15:39.314
Now maybe you're still trying to figure out what baptism really is, whether it's even necessary or why it matters, maybe something has even been blocking you from fully hearing what God says about it.

15:40.175 --> 15:48.626
Or maybe you didn't even realize that something was missing at all, but today your eyes and your ears are about to be opened.

15:49.282 --> 15:52.347
That happened to me recently in a very literal way.

15:52.407 --> 15:54.811
Earlier this year, I went in for a full physical.

15:54.851 --> 15:57.355
Two days, every test imaginable.

15:57.395 --> 16:00.100
Thankfully, everything came back mostly healthy, positive.

16:00.140 --> 16:05.128
At the very end, my doctor casually said, did you know you have a ton of earwax?

16:06.490 --> 16:07.532
I said, no, I don't.

16:07.652 --> 16:09.755
I cleaned my ears that morning.

16:09.775 --> 16:10.316
That was true.

16:10.356 --> 16:11.298
He asked with what?

16:12.039 --> 16:12.960
I said with Q-tips.

16:13.802 --> 16:16.466
Now, he looked at me like I had just confessed a crime.

16:16.898 --> 16:20.582
He said Q-tips are the worst things you can use in your ears.

16:21.163 --> 16:24.768
They don't clean your ears, they pack the wax in deeper.

16:25.528 --> 16:37.062
Now they should write that on the box, at least in bigger print, apparently it is on the box, but fine print now, apparently too, the entire world knows that Q-tips are a scam for cleaning out the earwax in your ears except for me.

16:37.883 --> 16:43.410
So they scheduled me for this very glamorous follow-up appointment called Earwax Removal.

16:44.066 --> 16:45.488
Sounds like I'm joking, I'm not.

16:45.548 --> 16:55.842
They put some hot water, high-powered vacuum, TV monitor so I could actually watch this microscopic camera, clean it all out, and I'll spare showing you the video of this.

16:55.902 --> 16:56.603
But guess what?

16:57.524 --> 16:59.707
This is true, immediately I could hear better.

16:59.747 --> 17:03.432
For years, I've been asking my wife, Emily, to speak up.

17:04.033 --> 17:11.563
It turns out there was something blocking my ability to hear, and I didn't even know it.

17:12.284 --> 17:13.586
See, I wanna suggest today,

17:14.018 --> 17:17.724
that for many people when it comes to baptism, something similar is happening.

17:18.686 --> 17:34.371
There's something blocking your ability to clearly hear and understand God's invitation to get baptized, not because you're resistant, not because you're hard-hearted, but because perhaps something unknowingly has been in the way.

17:35.392 --> 17:41.362
And today is about removing whatever is blocking that step for some of you, today is the day.

17:41.954 --> 17:45.719
that you step into these waters and declare, I can hear now.

17:46.821 --> 17:47.322
I get it.

17:48.083 --> 17:51.468
Jesus has changed my life and I'm not turning back.

17:52.089 --> 17:59.780
Today is the day that you are gonna leave the old life behind and walk out of here spiritually refreshed, renewed, and transformed in Christ.

18:00.501 --> 18:04.406
I wanna take us to Acts chapter two, found in the New Testament right after the four gospels.

18:05.267 --> 18:09.874
