And so more people start

19:07.970 --> 19:11.656
gathering, and then something even more supernatural happens.

19:12.437 --> 19:23.914
Even though the disciples are speaking in their own native language, every person in the crowd can understand what's being prayed, sung, and spoken no matter what language they personally spoke.

19:23.934 --> 19:27.139
And so this moment becomes known as Pentecost.

19:28.001 --> 19:33.749
