And so Peter, one of the disciples, stands up with the other disciples and says, listen carefully, these people aren't drunk.

19:55.782 --> 19:57.083
It's only 9 a.m. in the morning.

19:57.924 --> 19:59.486
No one is drunk at the 9 a.m. service.

